column2: Some individual was kind enough to "donate" [GetGrammaticalNumberThisThese] [This.GetName] to soldiers of [target_raiding_ruler.GetTitledFirstName] when they arrived in [target_looted_holding.GetName]. Locals did not hear about that person ever since.

By the right of might, [target_raiding_ruler.GetTitledFirstName] become the lawful owner of [GetGrammaticalNumberThisThese] [This.GetName] after [target_raiding_ruler.GetHerHis] army sacked [target_looted_holding.GetName].

Once upon a time, in [target_looted_holding.GetName] lived a man who thought that resistance to evil by force is morally wrong. Unfortunately for him, troops of [target_raiding_ruler.GetTitledFirstName] did not care about that when they took [GetGrammaticalNumberThisThese] [This.GetName] from his dead body.

A poor widow that lived in [target_looted_holding.GetName] did not sell [GetGrammaticalNumberThisThese] [This.GetName] in order to get some food only because [GetGrammaticalNumberItThey] [GetGrammaticalNumberWasWere] the last memento of her husband. When raiders of [target_raiding_ruler.GetTitledFirstName] come, they send that widow to her husband.

Some people tell that subordinates of [target_raiding_ruler.GetTitledFirstName], used "the supreme authority from which all other authorities are derived" to get [GetGrammaticalNumberThisThese] [This.GetName] when they were in [target_looted_holding.GetName]. Other people tell that these subordinates just used violence.

Population of [target_looted_holding.GetName] no longer can voice their complaints about expropriation of [GetGrammaticalNumberThisThese] [This.GetName] in favour of [target_raiding_ruler.GetTitledFirstName], even if they wanted to.
Looters of [target_raiding_ruler.GetTitledFirstName] found [GetGrammaticalNumberThisThese] [This.GetName] when they pillaged [target_looted_holding.GetName].

Caravan that was resting in [target_looted_holding.GetName] carried [GetGrammaticalNumberThisThese] [This.GetName] among their cargo. Due to orders of [target_raiding_ruler.GetTitledFirstName], caravaneers were put to eternal rest and artifact[GetGrammaticalNumberEndingPluralS] [GetGrammaticalNumberWasWere] put to [target_raiding_ruler.GetHerHis] treasury.
